is measure will not last long.\"</p><p>While more difficult, it is still technically possible to get around the ban if users can make it appear that they are accessing Twitter from outside Turkey. Twitter refused to comment, but it is understood to be aware of the development.</p>","headline":"Turkey steps up bid to block Twitter after users flout ban","trailText":"Move follows threats from Turkish prime minister Recep Tayyip Erdogan that he would 'root out' the social media network","thumbnail":"http://static.guim.co.uk/sys-images/Guardian/Pix/pictures/2014/3/23/1395617745576/Turkish-Prime-Minister-Re-003.jpg","wordcount":"279","liveBloggingNow":"false","commentCloseDate":"2014-03-26T23:38:06Z"},"webUrl":"http://www.theguardian.com/world/2014/mar/23/turkey-twitter-ban","apiUrl":"http://beta.content.guardianapis.com/world/2014/mar/23/turkey-twitter-ban","tags":[{"id":"world/turkey","webTitle":"Turkey","type":"keyword","sectionId":"world","sectionName":"World news","webUrl":"http://www.theguardian.com/world/turkey","apiUrl":"http://beta.content.guardianapis.com/world/turkey","references":[]},{"id":"world/world","webTitle":"World news","type":"keyword","sectionId":"world","sectionName":"World news","webUrl":"http://www.theguardian.com/world/world","apiUrl":"http://beta.content.guardianapis.com/world/world","references":[]},{"id":"technology/twitter","webTitle":"Twitter","type":"keyword","sectionId":"technology","sectionName":"Technology","webUrl":"http://www.theguardian.com/technology/twitter","apiUrl":"http://beta.content.guardianapis.com/technology/twitter","references":[]},{"id":"media/media","webTitle":"Media","type":"keyword","sectionId":"media","sectionName":"Media","webUrl":"http://www.theguardian.com/media/media","apiUrl":"http://beta.content.guardianapis.com/media/media","references":[]},{"id":"technology/internet","webTitle":"Internet","type":"keyword","sectionId":"technology","sectionName":"Technology","webUrl":"http://www.theguardian.com/technology/interne