b at TurkStat, known in Turkey as Tüik.</p><p>\"The incident was not a terrorist attack,\" the Hürriyet daily website quoted  Tepe as saying. \"The attacker's name was Veysi Erin. He worked as a psychologist at Tüik.\" A Tüik official confirmed  that seven people had died and one person had been slightly wounded, but provided no further details.</p><p>Tüik's local manager was among those killed in the attack, Hürriyet said on its website.</p><p>Political tensions are high in Turkey this month ahead of local elections on 30 March  and amid a corruption scandal dogging prime minister Recep Tayyip Erdoğan's government.</p>","headline":"Sacked state employee shoots six dead at Turkish Statistical Institute","trailText":"Psychologist dismissed from his job at TurkStat kills local manager and five others before turning the gun on himself","thumbnail":"http://static.guim.co.uk/sys-images/Guardian/Pix/pictures/2014/3/19/1395220399923/Turkish-PM-Recep-Tayyip-E-004.jpg","wordcount":"141","liveBloggingNow":"false","commentCloseDate":"2014-03-22T09:21:58Z"},"webUrl":"http://www.theguardian.com/world/2014/mar/19/state-employee-kills-turkey-statistical-institute-shoot-turkstat","apiUrl":"http://beta.content.guardianapis.com/world/2014/mar/19/state-employee-kills-turkey-statistical-institute-shoot-turkstat","tags":[{"id":"world/turkey","webTitle":"Turkey","type":"keyword","sectionId":"world","sectionName":"World news","webUrl":"http://www.theguardian.com/world/turkey","apiUrl":"http://beta.content.guardianapis.com/world/turkey","references":[]},{"id":"world/recep-tayyip-erdogan","webTitle":"Recep Tayyip Erdogan","type":"keyword","sectionId":"world","sectionName":"World news","webUrl":"http://www.theguardian.com/world/recep-tayyip-erdogan","apiUrl":"http://beta.content.guardianapis.com/world/recep-tayyip-erdogan","references":[]},{"id":"world/world","webTitle":"World news","type":"keyword","sectionId":"world","sectionName":"World news","webUrl":"http://www.theguardian.com/world/wor